<div class="credit first">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>作品名称：</strong>至深的婚礼</p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pimpernel-f-wagner" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2844512); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2844512&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663841" alt="Pimpernel_F_Wagner" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2844512)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pimpernel-f-wagner" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2844512); return false;">Pimpernel_F_Wagner</a></span></p>
<p><strong>该作者的更多作品：</strong><a href="/pimpernel">作者页在此。</a></p>
